{"id":"837de5954e9b2d12697bb5c8522b2751bd039ec1","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1228362","title":"如果一个 claude 号被 ban，那用过这个号的 pc 是否也被标黑了？","site_name":"Info Flow","source":"V2EX (创意工作者社区)","byline":"blackantt","excerpt":"程序员 - @blackantt - 想买个成品号来试一下。 但是如果被 ban ，是否 pc 也会被拉黑？","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div id=\"Wrapper\">\n                \n                \n<div><p>想买个成品号来试一下。 但是如果被 ban ，是否 pc 也会被拉黑？</p></div>\n\n<!-- SOL tip topic -->\n\n\n\n\n\n<div>\n    <div><P><a href=\"/tag/Ban\"><li></li> Ban</a><a href=\"/tag/PC\"><li></li> PC</a><a href=\"/tag/账号\"><li></li> 账号</a></P><p><span>11 replies &#160;<strong>•</strong> &#160;2026-07-20 10:38:31 +08:00</span>\n    </p></div>\n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17880895\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/5abcf4a997041bfdf9905c4772aba38c?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"bbxx11\" data-uid=\"676965\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>1</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/bbxx11\">bbxx11</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 17:49:54 +08:00\">21h 21m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>现在不是随便注册吗？我之前被 ban 的 现在又注册了一个 目前正常</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17880977\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0e09/5e05/1183_normal.png?m=1708966496\" alt=\"ETiV\" data-uid=\"1183\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>3</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/ETiV\">ETiV</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 18:52:08 +08:00\">20h 19m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>抓过 Claude Code 请求，metadata 里面是有 device_id 字段的，所以……不排除</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881098\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d1f2/b9b4/64727_normal.png?m=1784360797\" alt=\"isbase\" data-uid=\"64727\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>4</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/isbase\">isbase</a></strong> &#160; <div><p>PRO</p></div>&#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 20:28:34 +08:00\">18h 42m ago via iPhone</span> \n                    \n                    <p>不光设备 id  连仓库 hash 都会上传</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881138\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/891f/c90e/499149_normal.png?m=1783070382\" alt=\"calvinHxx\" data-uid=\"499149\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>5</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/calvinHxx\">calvinHxx</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 20:52:30 +08:00\">18h 18m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>不会，帐号被 ban 直接 delelte 过一会就可以用样的帐号注册了。不过用一段时间还是会被封 。</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881141\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/479c/3b11/41753_normal.png?m=1756537907\" alt=\"Cu635\" data-uid=\"41753\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>6</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/Cu635\">Cu635</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 20:53:04 +08:00\">18h 18m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>间谍软件大概率会上传设备指纹的。</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881198\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/11ca/59d7/632236_normal.png?m=1749454732\" alt=\"woodchen\" data-uid=\"632236\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>7</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/woodchen\">woodchen</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 21:31:06 +08:00\">17h 40m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>处理下`.claude`目录内的文件, 清空后就好了.</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881251\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6bcd38315512e83088cf7d9204033716?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"jakychen\" data-uid=\"81503\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>8</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/jakychen\">jakychen</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 22:07:25 +08:00\">17h 4m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>其实现在选择这么多了，海外 codex 已经能够顶得上 claude 了，封禁不怎么封<br>kimi glm 也能够匹配能用了，没必要贴着不让你用的产品一直用</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17881900\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9957/cdcc/347966_normal.png?m=1756265795\" alt=\"xyooyx\" data-uid=\"347966\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>9</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/xyooyx\">xyooyx</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-20 09:34:34 +08:00\">5h 36m ago